      • map

        public final <S> JBTreeTraverser<S> map(Function<? super T,? extends S> function)
        Returns a JBTreeTraverser that applies function to each element of this traverser. The required reverse transform, a hash map, is built internally while traversing. Prefer map(Function, Function) if a cheap reverse transform is available.
